rent disciplinary backgrounds (including literary theory, other medieval literatures and anthropology). Speaker and Authority interrogates important questions about the concept of knowledge, as well as its role in medieval Scandinavian society and its broader European cultural context.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aEddasxHistory and criticism. 0aOld Norse poetryxHistory and criticism. 0aWisdom in literature. 4aAltnordisch/Sprache. 4aEdda. 4aSkandinavien/Mittelalter. 4aSkandinavische Mythologie. 4aWeisheitsliteratur. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / English, Irish, Scottish, Welsh.2bisacsh  aOld Norse.  aScandinavian mythology.  aViking and medieval Scandinavia.  aeddic poetry.  awisdom literature.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE ENGLISH 2017z978311062526408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2017z9783110548198oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97831105483100 cprintz978311054817440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311054979940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110549799423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110549799/original  a978-3-11-062526-4  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE ENGLISH 2017b2017  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076249-5  DG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles